snippet.title: No Water In Hell | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
There is literally, like actually, seriously, honestly, NOT A SHRED OF DOUBT, THAT THERE IS ACTUALLY NO WATER IN HELL!!!!

Support us on Kickstarter!
https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/caffnight/no-water-in-hell

Try out the game now on our itch.io!
https://caffnight.itch.io/no-water-in-hell

No Water In Hell is a new game being developed by CaffNight Software. An all new roguelite adventure where you delve deeper into the circles of hell, extinguishing evil, one fire hydrant at a time


Don't forget to check out our other socials:
DISCORD - https://discord.gg/cAC8XQmAwn
TWITTER - https://twitter.com/caffnight
FACEBOOK - https://www.facebook.com/CaffNight
